WEBVTT

00:13:58.609 --> 00:14:00.405
"That's a beautiful mind."

00:14:01.483 --> 00:14:05.690
This, this is the beauty
that can change people

00:14:05.714 --> 00:14:06.912
into better people,

00:14:06.936 --> 00:14:10.256
by switching a special light
in their eyes.

00:14:10.672 --> 00:14:13.387
And making buildings for this beauty

00:14:13.411 --> 00:14:16.093
makes cities better places to live.

00:14:16.863 --> 00:14:18.409
And better cities

00:14:19.196 --> 00:14:21.102
make better citizens.

00:14:22.244 --> 00:14:25.148
Well, this beauty --

00:14:25.172 --> 00:14:27.751
this universal beauty, I should say --

00:14:29.014 --> 00:14:32.480
is one of the few things
that can change the world.